snippet.title: Cannelé & Nomnom — Defective Agency (Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW: https://pyrofoux.itch.io/defective-agency
Follow a duo of disastrous detectives while they investigate those three mysteries:

🔎 Who are you?
✨ What's your magical Gift?
👁️‍ What happened to your memories?

Coming out in December 2022, on https://pyrofoux.itch.io
Made by DISASTER DUO (Yazaleea and Younès Rabii)

Follow our Twitter for release updates: https://twitter.com/Disaster_Duo

~ Trailer credits ~
* Character illustrations by Arisae (https://twitter.com/arisae_art)
* OST composed by LSKR (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCU_Qf8irqFSIj4QOI1s_-2Q)
* Cat's illustration by Calvin Arium
